snippet.title: Three Days to Kill Official Trailer + Trailer Review : HD PLUS
snippet.description:
Three Days to Kill debuts its official trailer for 2014 featuring Kevin Costner and Amber Heard!  Watch it today with a trailer review!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Three Days to Kill debuts its official trailer for 2014 and you can see it here today plus get a trailer review!  Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph gives you her reaction to this trailer for Three Days to Kill starring Kevin Costner and Amber Heard, from Luc Besson!  And with Beyond The Trailer's Trailer Plus, you'll get a link to other movie news, reviews, and trailers!  Enjoy this official HD trailer and trailer review for Three Days to Kill before you see the full movie in 2014!  And make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for entertainment news on YouTube today!
